query:
SELECT
                    result AS "result: sqlx::types::Json<Box<RawValue>>",
                    result_columns,
                    created_by AS "created_by!"
                FROM v2_job_completed c
                    JOIN v2_job USING (id)
                WHERE c.id = $1 AND c.workspace_id = $2 AND ($3::text[] IS NULL OR tag = ANY($3))
